---
title: "US13 — Manually enter workout details"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ManualEntryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>StartWorkoutSession / EndWorkoutSession
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>WorkoutGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: enter type, duration, metrics
  B->>C: save manual session (no device)
  C->>G: insert + rpc end_workout_session
  note right of G: connected_device_id = null<br/>marks a manual entry
  G-->>C: xp_gained
  C-->>B: saved
  B-->>A: session appears in History
